  - Emergency contact for the '98 K2 Expedition. I remember the mountain. I remember
    the storm. I remember the rope.
  - Beneficiary for offshore account 4014. There was money going somewhere every
    month. I told myself I didn't know where.
  - Date of my proudest moment. The guitar is in the corner. I should look at the
    guitar.
